
 XTreme Racing Patch
---------------------

Version 1.01 : Fixes problems on Microbotics boards but *not* Warp Engine 040 Boards

This patch contains 5 files :

This Patch Readme
An XTR FAQ
A replacement Readme for Disk 3
race
frontend

To use the patch simply copy the race and frontend files over the existing ones.
Then delete the 'nomusic' file if it exists.

Users who currently have no problems do not need this patch.


